5.10 Queue Connection Factory Setup
About this task
To configure the XA Queue Connection Factory, complete the following steps:
Procedure
1.
Navigate to <DomainName> > Services > Messaging > JMS Modules;
2.
Click on op-jms in JMS Modules list;
3.
Click the New button inside the Configuration tab;
4.
Select Type “Connection Factory” and click Next;
5.
Set the following fields:
Name : “CuramQueueConnectionFactory”
JNDIName : “jms/CuramQueueConnectionFactory”;
6.
Click the Next button;
7.
Click the Finish button;
8.
Click the “CuramQueueConnectionFactory” just configured;
